<section class="ox-rules ox-hidden">
    <div>
        <h1>How to play</h1>
        <p>Flip the card to find the matches.</p>
        <p>You have one minute and <b>6 couples</b> of animals to detect!</p>
    </div>
    <img class="button" src="https://www.grupoabsa.com/web/image/9574487/NEXT.png"
        alt="Next button" />
</section>

<section class="ox-scoring ox-hidden">
    <div>
        <p>For each match you will get <b>100 points.</b></p>
        <p>If you find all the matches between:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><b>50-60</b> seconds you get additional <b>50 points</b></li>
            <li><b>40-50</b> seconds you will get additional <b>75 points</b></li>
            <li><b>0-40</b> seconds you will get additional <b>100 points</b></li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <img class="button" src="https://www.grupoabsa.com/web/image/9574491/PLAY.png"
        alt="Play button" />
</section>

